MATT: She takes the stone. "Yes!" The Lady's
blessing upon you all. She spins around, drops the

03:22:03.538 --> 03:22:12.796
stone in the pot and begins stirring it. "Stone
soup for meal tonight! Flavored well with victory.

03:22:12.796 --> 03:22:17.430
"You've earned a fine meal, my goblins!"

03:22:17.430 --> 03:22:22.751
(cheering)

03:22:22.751 --> 03:22:29.311
MATT: As she pours you all your evening's meal of
boom-boom stone soup, you recount the tales of the

03:22:29.311 --> 03:22:35.209
horrible slaughter that befell those who walked in
your path. You realize you managed to bring back a

03:22:35.209 --> 03:22:37.960
trench coat as part of your victory prize.

03:22:37.960 --> 03:22:40.647
PHIL: Stir in a little bit of dried meat with it.

03:22:40.647 --> 03:22:44.941
IVAN: We throw it on top of our trophy pile.

03:22:44.941 --> 03:22:46.950
TALIESIN: And an empty snuff box tin.

03:22:46.950 --> 03:22:51.288
MARISHA: And some poo and some bottles for molotov
cocktails.

03:22:51.288 --> 03:22:53.535
MATT: A masterful bounty you've collected this
evening.

03:22:53.535 --> 03:22:55.820
IVAN: I cast Grease on all of us.

03:22:55.820 --> 03:23:00.330
MARISHA: Slip'n'Slide!

03:23:00.330 --> 03:23:08.160
MATT: Freeze frame credit roll. (singing) Anyway
you want, that's the way you need it. And that is

03:23:08.160 --> 03:23:15.215
your game tonight, your one-shot Pathfinder game.
Big thank you, once again, to Paizo and to

03:23:15.215 --> 03:23:20.557
Syrinscape for helping us put this together, for
bringing the prizes for our fantastic audience.

03:23:20.557 --> 03:23:27.408
Thank you all for watching this wondrously chaotic
goblin spree that transpired. Big round of

03:23:27.408 --> 03:23:30.290
applause for our players this evening. You did
amazing.

03:23:30.290 --> 03:23:33.997
PHIL: Pure, unadulterated Id.

03:23:33.997 --> 03:23:42.627
IVAN: Seriously, #TeamLeftSide. For all of the
