03:23:57.635 --> 03:23:58.669
MATT: Yeah.

03:23:58.669 --> 03:23:59.781
ASHLY: Oh my god.

03:23:59.781 --> 03:24:01.937
MARISHA: The ones that are always in the books?

03:24:01.937 --> 03:24:03.242
MATT: In the books, yeah!

03:24:03.242 --> 03:24:04.706
ASHLY: That's amazing!

03:24:04.706 --> 03:24:08.123
MATT: The actual Pathfinder Iconic characters!

03:24:08.123 --> 03:24:09.442
MARISHA: We killed Pathfinder!

03:24:09.442 --> 03:24:11.193
ASHLY: Yay! We murdered it!

03:24:11.193 --> 03:24:13.519
MARISHA: These people, yeah!

03:24:13.519 --> 03:24:15.857
TALIESIN: I was prepared to go down in a blaze of
glory.

03:24:15.857 --> 03:24:17.464
ASHLY: Yeah, me too! I thought we were all
going to die.

